organization.description: United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) in Pakistan. OCHA brings together humanitarian actors to ensure a coherent response to emergencies in Pakistan, and to establish a framework within which each actor can contribute to the overall response effort.
